Title: Assault on the Wellspring
Description:
Terro gave his life to protect the Dream. Which means we must see it through.

Vyranoth should be able to handle Lethka, we must find Suzska.

I hope Lethka did not attack her first. We should start looking near the Wellspring. 

Meet me there so we can continue our search.
ObjectivesText: Spy on the Wellspring of Life with Buri.
